Package: bayesmodmed
Title: Bayesian Moderated Mediation Tutorial
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bryan", "Gibson", , "bgibson@usi.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Companion code for "Bayesian Moderated Mediation Analysis:
    A Step-by-Step Guide" published in Psychological Methods. Provides
    complete R code for conducting Bayesian moderated mediation analysis
    (first-stage moderation; Hayes Model 8) using the brms package.
